metadata.name: Duotone | Aqua + Red
metadata.description:
Type: Generative Art
Edition: 1/1 from the Amorphous Symmetry collection
Size: 2500x2500
Year: 2022

An endless drowsy dance flows along the silky curves that once came into existence by the motion of 8 circles rotating around each other.

Circle Radii & Frequencies:
[0.18, 0.06, 0.08, 0.16, 0.14, 0.18, 0.16, 0.04]
[7, 1, 25, 7, -11, 25, 7, -17]

Created by Nadieh Bremer
